data.description: $7,000 towards buying down your interest rate. Welcome to your new haven in the highly sought-after Panther Creek community! This stunning 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom residence is a perfect blend of comfort and style. From the moment you step through the door, you're greeted by an inviting open flex space, ideal for entertaining friends or creating a cozy family haven. The main level hosts a spacious owner's suite, offering a private retreat for relaxation. With 3 additional bedrooms upstairs, there's ample space for family, guests, or a home office. You will be blown away by the upgraded wood floors upstairs and tile downstairs. The heart of the home, the kitchen, boasts 42'' cabinets and granite countertops, providing both functionality and elegance. It seamlessly opens to the living room, creating a bright and welcoming space filled with natural light. Host countless gatherings with friends and family in the generously sized fenced backyard. Whether it's a weekend barbecue or a quiet evening under the stars, this outdoor space is perfect for creating lasting memories. Conveniently located near NAS Jax, hospitals and schools. Don't miss your chance to make this beautiful property your new home sweet home in Panther Creek.
